OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FYvette Fielding says she   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwas bullied on Blue Peter  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, TV presenter Yvette Fielding, who made 
OL,6, headlines as the youngest-ever host of 
OL,7, Blue Peter, has claimed she was bullied
OL,8, while making the show, and almost quit.
OL,10,FThe host, who was 18 when she joined   
OL,11,Fthe BBC kids' TV show, said she was    
OL,12,F"pushed to the limit" by behaviour that
OL,13,Fleft her a "shaking, gibbering wreck." 
OL,15,FShe added that if a young presenter    
OL,16,Ftoday faced similar conditions "there'd
OL,17,Fbe quite a few implications to that".  
OL,19,FThe BBC said it would not be commenting
OL,20,Fon her allegations.                    
